headline: Meet Norton Neo: The First Safe AI-Native Browser Now in Early Access
summary: Today, Norton, a trusted brand part of Gen (NASDAQ: GEN), unveiled its new, innovative browser designed from the ground up with advanced artificial intelligence, Norton Neo. Neo brings together a powerful combination of AI-native intelligence and world-class safety protection, making it the first browser truly built to reimagine how we experience the web with a safer, smarter internet.
